@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam handwritten false

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ActorBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderColor #999999
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F0F0F0
    ParticipantBorderColor #333333
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ParticipantFontName Arial
    ParticipantFontSize 12
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActorFontSize 12
}

title 在线聊天时序图

actor "用户A" as UserA
participant "H5前端A" as H5A
participant "H5前端B" as H5B
actor "用户B" as UserB
participant "REST API" as API
participant "WebSocket服务" as WS
participant "数据库" as DB

== 1. 发起聊天 ==

UserA -> H5A: 点击"聊一聊"
activate H5A

H5A -> API: POST /conversations
activate API

API -> DB: 查询或创建conversation
activate DB

DB --> API: 返回会话数据
deactivate DB

API --> H5A: 返回会话ID
deactivate API

H5A -> H5A: 跳转到聊天详情页

== 2. WebSocket连接建立 ==

H5A -> WS: 连接 ws://host/ws?token=xxx
activate WS

WS -> WS: 验证Token

WS --> H5A: auth:success

H5A -> WS: subscribe conversation_id

WS --> H5A: subscribe:success

deactivate WS

== 3. 用户B进入聊天 ==

UserB -> H5B: 打开消息页面
activate H5B

H5B -> API: GET /conversations/:id
activate API

API --> H5B: 返回会话详情
deactivate API

H5B -> WS: 连接WebSocket
activate WS

H5B -> WS: subscribe conversation_id

deactivate WS
deactivate H5B

== 4. 发送消息 ==

UserA -> H5A: 输入消息内容

UserA -> H5A: 点击发送

H5A -> API: POST /conversations/:id/messages
activate API

API -> API: 验证会话权限

API -> DB: 保存消息到messages集合
activate DB

DB --> API: 返回消息ID
deactivate DB

API -> DB: 更新会话last_message
activate DB

deactivate DB

API --> H5A: 返回创建的消息
deactivate API

H5A -> H5A: 显示在消息列表

== 5. 实时推送 ==

API -> WS: notifyConversationParticipants
activate WS

WS -> H5B: message:new
activate H5B

H5B -> H5B: 显示新消息

H5B -> API: POST /conversations/:id/read
activate API

API -> DB: 更新未读数
activate DB

deactivate DB

API -> WS: conversation:read

WS -> H5A: 对方已读通知
deactivate WS
deactivate API
deactivate H5B

== 6. 心跳保活 ==

H5A -> WS: ping
activate WS

WS --> H5A: pong
deactivate WS

== 7. 断线重连 ==

H5A -> WS: 连接断开
activate WS

deactivate WS

H5A -> H5A: 定时重连(2.5秒)

H5A -> WS: 重新连接
activate WS

deactivate WS
deactivate H5A

@enduml
